WEBVTT

00:01:28.600 --> 00:01:30.424
Oge mbu m nuru maka "isi izu oke,"

00:01:31.214 --> 00:01:34.219
E sim Ghana puta ohuu,
banye na Ulo akwukwo e be obibi,

00:01:34.219 --> 00:01:36.015
a kporo Peddie 
di na New Jersey.

00:01:38.935 --> 00:01:43.399
A kam gabigara iru uju
nmadu asaa ndi

00:01:43.409 --> 00:01:46.394
nwuru n' otu onwa.

00:01:46.569 --> 00:01:48.025
Onye n'eleta ndi ahu n'adighi,


00:01:48.049 --> 00:01:52.113
k' ometuru gbasara ihe m na-agabiga
--Chukwu gozie mkpuruobi ya--

00:01:52.137 --> 00:01:54.567
o juru m gbasara isi izu oke m.

00:01:55.426 --> 00:01:57.409
m juom onwe si, "ara a na-ayi ya?"

00:01:58.214 --> 00:02:00.658
O makwa n'abu m dimkpa Africa?